          .col-half.col-half-right.section-about__text
            %h3 Who we are
            %p.paragraph-margin Welcome to Edit Salon based in Aughton cum Aston, Sheffield, situated 5 minutes drive from Junction 33 off the M1. Specialising in Hair, Makeup and Nails, Edit tailors each service to suit every individual. Our creators at Edit hold the highest standard of qualifications in their fields and attend regular training each year to maintain the highest standard. We pride ourselves in customer service to make your stay with us an unforgettable one. This urban contemporary salon is one of a kind!

